Class ScoreData

java.lang.Object
javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
Snake.ScoreData
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Iterable<Score>, Collection<Score>, TableModel
public class ScoreData extends AbstractTableModel implements Collection<Score>
The Score data class. This class represents a collection of scores and implements the Collection interface.
